tags: the pokémon are such a highlight in this game so far honestly
i get so excited whenever i see one
i love this whole thing of pokémon being incorporated into regular society it's so good
the burmy's voices are so adorable...
mightyena and ludicolo being female is cool since pokémon games don't tend to stray from typical gender presentation expectations very much
that one scene where ludicolo just dances and sings while walking away after giving tim and pikachu their coffee...
i love her so much. best character in the game
detective pikachu himself is pretty great too of course
him just clutching his back in pain after doing a minimal amount of exercise is definitely relatable lol
caption: i… love these pokémon introductions

@charmander-propaganda 
Hello! It’s @cyndaganda and @raichu-propaganda here. I thought you might like these shots of charmander...
body:
@charmander-propaganda

Hello! It’s @cyndaganda and @raichu-propaganda here. I thought you might like these shots of charmander from the Detective Pikachu Trailer!

Bulbasaur may have gotten the spotlight treatment but let’s not forget that charmander is the first Pokémon we get a clear look at! Look at the little guy!

We even see him helping a dude cook something later in the trailer! That is both cute and clever! Little details like that give me hope for this movie.

Do you have any thoughts or hopes for it? I’ve personally been wanting something like this since I was 3.

summary: In 2019 we’re going to get the first games in the 8th Generation of Pokémon, as well as the respective anime adaption once Sun...
body:
In 2019 we’re going to get the first games in the 8th Generation of Pokémon, as well as the respective anime adaption once Sun and Moon wraps up, a CG remake of Mewtwo Strikes back, and our very first live-action Pokémon movie… based on Detective Pikachu.

It’s going to be one of the most INTERESTING years in the franchises history no matter how all these things actually turn out through sheer novelty.
